    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Mohsus fazzija ue Waraiis: Labbis laid tas Gohds teu irr/ ne ka man/ kurrâ Laikâ buhs man tewis deht/ un tawo Kalpu/ un tawo Lauschu labbad tuhgt/ ka tahm Wardehm no te- wim/un no tawa Namma buhs isdeldehain tapt/ ka wiſtas Up- pê ween paleek.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un wiſsch fazzija : Rihtu. Un tas fazzija / lai tas ta irr pehz tawn Wahrdn / tadeht ka tew buhs sunnaht / ka ne weens tam KUNGAU innhſu Deewam lih- dsa effus/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad buhs tahm Wardehm atkahpt no tew / un no tawa Namma / un no taweem Kal- peem / un no taweem Laudim/ Uppê ween buhs tahni palikt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad isgahje Mohsus un Aïrons no Waraiis/ un Mohsus fanze ue to KUNGU to Warschu deht/ ka wiſsch Waraiim bij ap- fohlijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tas KUNGS darrija pehz Mohsus Wahrdn / un tahs Wardes nomirre Nammoſs / Muischâs un Tihrumoſs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee mette tahs Rohpâs/ un ta Semne ſmirdeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Rad nu Waraiis redſeja / ka wiſsch Atspirgschanu bij dab- bujis/ tad apzeetinaja wiſsch fa- wu Sirdi/ un ne klaufija teem/\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Kl us Mohsu: Sakti Adro steep tawu Sisli / un ti Semmes Pihſchlus/ka Ut wiſſa Egiptes-Semmê / darrija ta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo Aärons isſtee Rohku ar fawu Sisli / tohs Semmes Pihſchlu dauds Uttu tappe pee Ji un pee Lohpeem / wiſſi E Pihſchli bija Uttis wiſſâ Semmê.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad darbojahs tee ji arri ta ar fawahm V nahm/ ka tee liktu Uttis na tee ne warreja; ta btja tiſ pee Zilwekeem un peem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tee ns Waraii : Schis irr Pirſſis / tomehr Waraii apzeetinajahs/ un wiſsch fija teem / itt ka tas Kl bij fazzijis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija tas Kl us Mohsu : Zeilees riht a stahw preefſch Waraiis / wiſsch isees pee ta Uhden runna ue to : Ta fat KUNGS: Atlaid mannu dis/ ka tee man warr kalpa\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo ja tu mannuſ ne atlaidiſi/ tad fuhtifchu fadus Ruklaimus pahr te pahr taweem Kalpeem / u taweem Laudin/un tawò mds / un wiſfadeein Rukk ouhs to Egipteu Nammi\n"
    }
  ],
